text: Johan August Ekman, born 26 November 1845, in Hjälstad, Sweden, dead 30 November 1913 in Uppsala, Sweden was the Church of Sweden Archbishop of Uppsala between 1900-1913. He also served as bishop of Västerås between 1898 and 1900. == References == Category:1845 births Category:1913 deaths Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
title: Johan August Ekman
